Retrieve information of a publication

Source: R/retrieve.R
retrieve_document.Rd

Tidy data from any document published on the BOE and BORME from the BOE.

retrieve_document(cve)

Arguments

cve

Character with the code of the document.

See also

Other functions to retrieve documents: retrieve_sumario()

Examples

xml  <- get_xml(query_xml("BOE-B-2017-5"))
xml2 <- get_xml(query_xml("BOE-A-2017-5"))
xml3 <- get_xml(query_xml("BOE-S-2017-5"))
xml4 <- get_xml(query_xml("BORME-S-2020-108"))
cve <- "BOE-A-2020-12109"
df <- retrieve_document(cve)

About rOpenSpain

rOpenSpain is a community of R enthusiasts whose ultimate goal is to create high-quality R packages for data mining public spanish open sources.
